{"tid":2027353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★賀23？青衣居屋未補價賣555萬　首錄呎價逾萬元","createTime":"2020-05-21T11:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T11:16:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"94cbd50fe9cca9a3fce1da84fa4bb1298fd2c7df","tid":2027353,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"青衣未補價第二市場再錄高價成交。美聯黃淑賢表示，區內居屋青泰苑A座中層7室，實用面積554方呎，開價560萬港元放盤，議價後僅減5萬元，獲綠表客以555萬元購入，呎價10,018元，屋苑第二市場呎價歷來首破1萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200521/bkn-20200521182347294-0521_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200521%2Fbkn-20200521182347294-0521_00842_001.html&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=958f135c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200521/bkn-20200521182347294-0521_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cd2de214d6edd90de7a34bf88e35c5d5d56cbd85","tid":2027353,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01248ca1e2c0bb2abd8ccfa858fe63c775253ac","tid":2027353,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZeZnVb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZeZnVb.jpg&h=2e849448&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}